(1) Callbacks Issues
---------------------
==> Callback Hell : Nested Callbacks
==> Difficult To Reason About: Can't To Follow The Code
==> Inversion Of Control


EX (Callback Hell)
----

	// Nested Callbacks
	getData(function(a){
	    getMoreData(a, function(b){
		getMoreData(b, function(c){ 
		    getMoreData(c, function(d){ 
			    getMoreData(d, function(e){ 
				    ...
				});
			});
		});
	    });
	});
	
	
